Jeffrey Mylett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeffrey_Mylett 0 Jeffrey Mylett (June 8, 1949 – May 7, 1986) was an American actor and songwriter. He was best known for his roles in both the stage and film productions of Godspell. Jeffrey_Mylett ( June_8_,_1949 – May_7_,_1986 ) was an_American_actor_and_songwriter .
